s of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/182551/', '', 'Pentosan polysulfate, Phenazopyridine, Alprostadil, Mirabegron, Acetohydroxamic acid, Yohimbine, Avanafil, Phenyl salicylate, Ammonium chloride, Dimethyl sulfoxide', '', 1767369485);
